  ./COVERAGE.md:506:| `io.helidon.common:helidon-common` | [4.3.4<br>- 4.5.1-M1](metadata/io.helidon.common/helidon-common/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Helidon Common provides shared utility APIs for Helidon projects, including builders, error collection, lazy values, weighted services, generic type helpers, size parsing, and Native Image support helpers. It supplies reusable Java infrastructure used across Helidon microservice libraries and applications.</details> | [100.0% (1/1 calls)](stats/io.helidon.common/helidon-common/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:507:| `io.helidon.common:helidon-common-buffers` | [4.3.4<br>- 4.5.1-M1](metadata/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-buffers/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Helidon Common Buffers provides byte-buffer abstractions and byte operation utilities used by Helidon components. It includes fixed, growing, composite, and read-only buffer data implementations along with readers, writers, ASCII helpers, and lazy string handling.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-buffers/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:508:| `io.helidon.common:helidon-common-config` | [4.3.4<br>- 4.5.1-M1](metadata/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-config/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Helidon Common Config provides immutable tree-structured configuration abstractions and values used by Helidon common components. It lets JVM code create or obtain configuration from providers, navigate keys and nodes, map values, and integrate configured services.</details> | [100.0% (0/0 calls)](stats/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-config/) |
  ./COVERAGE.md:509:| `io.helidon.common:helidon-common-configurable` | [4.3.4<br>- 4.5.1-M1](metadata/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-configurable/index.json) | <details><summary>Show</summary> Helidon Common Configurable provides Java utilities that can be configured through Helidon common configuration, including thread pools, resources, allow lists, and cache helpers. It is a core Helidon support module used by other Helidon components to construct configurable runtime resources.</details> | [100.0% (1/1 calls)](stats/io.helidon.common/helidon-common-configurable/) |
