es and registry support for describing Helidon features and their metadata. It is shared by Helidon feature code generation and runtime components, including feature flavor, status, deprecation, and AOT metadata handling.\",\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features-metadata/index.json:18:      \"io.helidon.common.features.metadata\"\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:4:    \"library\": \"io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata:4.3.4\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:51:      \"library\": \"io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata:4.3.4\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:52:      \"summary\": \"No extra Maven dependency or Docker image is needed, but meaningful tests must provide Helidon metadata resources and avoid native-image-incompatible classpath scanning.\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:54:      \"agent_guidance\": \"Create synthetic test resources under `src/test/resources/META-INF/helidon`, such as `manifest` plus one or more known metadata files like `service.loader`, `service-registry.json`, `feature-registry.json`, or `config-metadata.json`. Exercise `MetadataDiscovery.create(MetadataDiscovery.Mode.RESOURCES)` directly, or set the system property `io.helidon.metadata.mode=RESOURCES` before using `MetadataDiscovery.instance()`. Do not rely on empty discovery or on `AUTO` choosing `SCANNING`, because the library documents scanning as unsuitable for native-image.\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:56:        \"The resolved artifact has zero runtime dependencies and its own jar does not contain `META-INF/helidon` metadata files to discover, so a default scaffold that only calls `list(...)` will likely cover only empty results.\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:57:        \"The artifact's embedded native-image resource config includes only `META-INF/helidon/manifest`; local native-image verification must confirm any synthetic test metadata resources are included as needed.\"\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:63:          \"summary\": \"#7781 Support for io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata:4.3.4; label=library-new-request; body_chars=39\"\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:75:      \"session_log_path\": \"/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge2/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/logs/io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata:4.3.4/library-preparation-preflight/pi-generation-2026-06-26T11-34-19-408436Z.log\"\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:90:      \"test_file\": \"tests/src/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/src/test/java/io_helidon_metadata/helidon_metadata/MetadataDiscoveryImplTest.java\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:91:      \"metadata_file\": \"metadata/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json\"\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata-hson/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:4:    \"library\": \"io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata-hson:4.3.4\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata-hson/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:45:      \"library\": \"io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata-hson:4.3.4\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata-hson/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:46:      \"summary\": \"The artifact is a small in-process HSON parser/writer with only normal transitive Helidon common dependencies; meaningful coverage is reachable using public APIs and in-memory streams without external services, extra dependencies, Docker, or environment setup.\",\n./stats/io.helidon.metadata/helidon-metadata-hson/4.3.4/execution-metrics.json:56:          \"summary\": \"#7793 Support for io.helidon.metadata:helidon-metadata-hson:4.3.4; label=library-new-request; bo