Helidon Common Features discovers and reports the Helidon features available on an application's class path for a selected Helidon flavor. It builds a feature tree from Helidon feature metadata and logs invalid, preview, deprecated, incubating, and native-image support information.\",\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/index.json:18:      \"io.helidon.common.features\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:5:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:11:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:19:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:25:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:27:      \"glob\" : \"META-INF/helidon/config-metadata.json\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:31:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:33:      \"glob\" : \"META-INF/helidon/feature-registry.json\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:37:        \"typeReached\" : \"io.helidon.common.features.FeatureCatalog\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:39:      \"glob\" : \"META-INF/helidon/media-types.properties\"\n./metadata/io.helidon.common.features/helidon-common-features/4.3.4/reachability-metadata.json:43